Klasse WinNT.SID_NAME_USE

java.lang.Object
com.sun.jna.platform.win32.WinNT.SID_NAME_USE
Umschließende Schnittstelle:
WinNT
public abstract static class WinNT.SID_NAME_USE extends Object
The SID_NAME_USE enumeration type contains values that specify the type of a security identifier (SID).
